latestReleaseNotes:
### Release info
Oobee is available as a desktop app for Mac and Windows. The setup files can be downloaded under `Assets` at the bottom of the page.

### Installation Guide
* Refer to the [Installation Guide](https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/blob/master/INSTALLATION.md) for Windows and Mac.

### What's New
#### Features
* Prevent Powershell-supported features from execution when Powershell blocked by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/pull/153

#### Improvements
* Clean up temporary files and log to storagePath by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/537
* Remove Powershell requirement by using tar.exe and reg.exe on Windows by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/539

#### Bug fixes
* Fix purple ai regex not matching certain patterns by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/534
* Resolve transient dependency flagged in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/pull/538
* Fix app crash due to outdated references and error log file by @younglim in https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/pull/155
